{"tid":516041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上大帽山等睇元旦日出 青年不適送院","createTime":"2018-01-01T03:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T02:53:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a9be11da4e82153098e0b012aa6913cce6988166","tid":516041,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>上大帽山等睇元旦日出 青年不適送院</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2018-01-01 09:18:01 HKT<br />\n<br />\n一名少年在荃灣大帽山雷達站通宵等看新一年第一度曙光，今早上山時卻身體不適，需要報警求助。18歲姓蔡青年與同學一行6人，昨日到大帽山睇日落，之後在山上通宵等睇日出，惟今晨6時21分上山頂時，懷疑低血糖感到不適，同行同學報警求助，蔡事後由救護車送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n專家建議，為了行山安全，出發前必須自我評估夜晚行山風險，有三大要點，其一是本身能力是否勝任，其二是否有足夠裝備，其三是行山路徑是否適合夜行。<br />\n<br />\n通宵行山等日出，夜行人士要考慮體能是否應付，並且有適合夜行裝備，因為夜晚行山較易疲倦，免疫能力會較低，所以一定要帶備足夠禦寒衣物，防止病倒。另外，照明裝備更加不可少，但不要依賴手機的電筒app，因不好拿，黑夜行山好易跌毀，應該帶箍在頭上的頭燈及手電筒，另可以帶埋行山手杖做盲公竹，免叉錯腳失足。"},{"pid":"40b06b1a255fa401bcacba9df9e7fed2394041d6","tid":516041,"uid":8867,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"781bdd8d96a128900d0d8839370b10345014fb6e","tid":516041,"uid":3253,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1194edd3ddab4f3596648b3719babfeafdcc6fd","tid":516041,"uid":143582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"18歲 學生應該係著唔夠衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又無準備定野食充飢"},{"pid":"81a0fa2faba737c54d9d5509ef63651d3325a1ef","tid":516041,"uid":15471,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"其實見暈使唔使即刻call車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無帶野咬既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家啲小朋友使唔使咁驚死，跳樓又見你地驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a52ce713b6995764ef895060beb7496902f509a","tid":516041,"uid":2613,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"大帽山只係行馬路都可以搞成咁<br />\n有冇咁撚渣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93552f974fd32b09b8c84d7111400c732ad892fa","tid":516041,"uid":48796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"預備不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcadfa158befdc0a9c84c1a6cbe82ff2b1087f4","tid":516041,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"根本係食唔夠卡路里去準備登山"},{"pid":"a982d5f427ddd7059c1b23d064246f1aa4cfac0b","tid":516041,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"eba7f52411cbf6fef6b07b2bd3d3f4d6a619223a","tid":516041,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"廢"},{"pid":"a4442da802e234c282b01ebe57b2d325734b310c","tid":516041,"uid":1067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"帶銀包，鎖匙，電話，尿袋就上山"},{"pid":"20425dbeb66f541d9ba8a3b39911168a64e98a10","tid":516041,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"要睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4120d26023efcf6fd6e9404cb31d9342727f617c","tid":516041,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"weak"},{"pid":"6568a0645bf1d1525836bd577ca0ce0a74ba722f","tid":516041,"uid":30522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"高山反應啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd89e7e6124967dbe37e54c28d96a56d9ad110d","tid":516041,"uid":1393